  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nThe root cause of this issue is similar to https://crbug.com/chromium/1355718, race condition UAF.  \n  \n\\*hci_cmd_sync_queue\\* will check the flag of hdev not equal to \\*HCI_UNREGISTER\\*[1], and enqueue \\*hdev->cmd_sync_work\\*(which is \\*hci_cmd_sync_work\\*)[2]. \\*hci"
}